{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sfyc23/EverydayWechat/issues/126","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sfyc23/EverydayWechat","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sfyc23/EverydayWechat/issues/126/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sfyc23/EverydayWechat/issues/126/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sfyc23/EverydayWechat/issues/126/events","html_url":"https://github.com/sfyc23/EverydayWechat/issues/126","id":458993195,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0NTg5OTMxOTU=","number":126,"title":"关于如何在服务器端扫描二维码登录的问题","user":{"login":"zxqfengdi","id":27198066,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI3MTk4MDY2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/27198066?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi","html_url":"https://github.com/zxqfengdi","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zxqfengdi/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2019-06-21T03:43:56Z","updated_at":"2019-06-30T10:17:11Z","closed_at":"2019-06-30T10:17:10Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"- 该项目的微信登录依靠Itchat模块，itchat模块默认支持在命令行模式显示二维码。\r\n\r\n![命令行二维码](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/27198066/59895837-b2b76480-9418-11e9-8033-9d357a77b9fc.png)\r\n\r\n- 但是该项目main目录下的hongmeng.py文件对登录时系统状态做了判断(注释部分)，代码如下：\r\n\r\n![二维码](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/27198066/59895431-2e181680-9417-11e9-8d2d-e7f63cf95d36.png)\r\n当os.environ.get('MODE')为'server'时才会在终端显示二维码。但是我ssh连接到服务器时发现os.environ里面根本没有MODE这个键，所以程序会默认打开二维码让我用手机扫描登录，这样ssh连接就会报错导致登录失败。\r\n\r\n- **解决方法**：不进行os.environ['MODE']值的判断，默认就在终端显示二维码就可以。代码修改在第二张图里面请参考。","closed_by":{"login":"sfyc23","id":7067207,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcwNjcyMDc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7067207?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23","html_url":"https://github.com/sfyc23","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sfyc23/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sfyc23/EverydayWechat/issues/126/reactions","total_count":3,"+1":3,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sfyc23/EverydayWechat/issues/126/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}